CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 3, 1962, pg. C3, reads: "Photos of Your Pittsburgh Story Rally - Missed Program - Sad because they had to miss the program because of the need to sell papers The Courier Courier's at the rally site were (left to ): Wanter Russell, Alton Dickson, Harold Washington, Steven Dickson, and Clyde Battles."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of man and boys holding special issue of Pittsburgh Courier Newspaper, including Wanter Russell, Alton Dickson, Harold Washington, Steven Dickson, and Clyde Battles, posed in Soldiers and Sailors Memorial Hall, for Pittsburgh Courier Newspaper's "Your Pittsburgh Story Rally"
